name: farm-house-4-bedroom
description: A spacious 25.6 x 15.05 meter farm-style single-level home designed for comfortable living and entertaining, featuring 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms arranged within a practical and well-balanced layout. At the heart of the home is a large great room that seamlessly combines the dining and living areas, creating an open and welcoming gathering space. The main kitchen is complemented by two outdoor kitchens, making it ideal for hosting events or enjoying alfresco dining. A dedicated laundry room and pantry enhance daily convenience and storage efficiency, while two fireplaces add warmth and character to the interior living spaces. The design also includes a front porch that enhances curb appeal and a back porch that extends the living area outdoors, providing relaxing views and additional space for family activities. A single-car garage completes the home with secure parking and functional storage.
